小豆的普通话水平提升得很快，从开始说普通话有些磕磕巴巴，到现在说起来逐渐流利，平舌翘舌等发音也越来越标准。 但谢女士的老公胡先生却有不同的意见，胡先生今年 29 岁，从事销售工作，是土生土长的重庆人。 胡先生表示，以前，小豆的重庆话说得还比较流利。现在小豆每天都在说普通话，没机会再说重庆话。久而久之，小豆普通话进步得很快，重庆话也丢得很快。 前不久，胡先生单独带小豆去爷爷奶奶家玩，爷爷奶奶让小豆说几句重庆话。然而，小豆已经完全说不利索了，直接说成了「椒盐版普通话」。 胡先生认为，孩子妈妈的教育方式有点偏激了，方言不应该丢掉，尤其是作为一名重庆人，能说一口流利的方言，也是一件很骄傲的事情。 很多市民和网友对此也有发表了自己的意见，你觉得孩子说普通话好还是方言好呢？"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ihq3XweqzptcqEAMaCDczMzg2ODU1IO2C3IwGMAU4VEAHcgk0OTk5NzQ4OTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"106 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-32401f1496dfb93da00a059ddc522f6d_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1637377718.4748206","card_id":"Q_498911444","target":{"id":498911444,"title":"长得帅的人，会喜欢上长得很普通的女孩子吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/498911444","type":"question","created":1636896159,"answer_count":175,"follower_count":230,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1818,3803,44472],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ihq3XweqzptcqEAMaCDczMTUwMzU2IJ+bxIwGMAA45gFACHIJNDk4OTExNDQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"103 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-76a430cb02dbd953c5fc01c473c0cb0f_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1637377718.4752262","card_id":"Q_500102170","target":{"id":500102170,"title":"2022 届高校毕业生规模预计 1076 万人，同比增加 167 万人，就业形势会如何？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/500102170","type":"question","created":1637310831,"answer_count":36,"follower_count":115,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[988,3789,11758,13306,105508],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":