的事实及罪名均无异议，并表示自愿认罪认罚。 杭州市富阳区人民法院认为： 被告人张德全、马敬华、张彦峰、韩祥、丁增泉、王国泉在生产、作业中违反有关安全管理规定，造成严重后果，其行为均已构成重大责任事故罪。各被告人均具有自首情节且自愿认罪认罚，依法予以从轻处罚，公诉机关提出的量刑建议适当，予以采纳，遂依法作出上述判决。杭州野生动物世界金钱豹脱逃案一审宣判，6人获刑"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ihq3XweqzptcqEAMaCDczMzk5NDkwIMzb3IwGMAQ4U0AKcgk1MDAwMzEzODJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"89 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-97fe4a264281089bfa180e63773dc563_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1637377718.4766827","card_id":"Q_499641902","target":{"id":499641902,"title":"《英雄联盟》中如果让你来重做皮城执法官蔚，你会怎么设计？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/499641902","type":"question","created":1637148071,"answer_count":21,"follower_count":31,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[18427,160274,400464],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4Ihq3XweqzptcqEAMaCDczMzEyNzUxIKfL04wGMAA4H0ALcgk0OTk2NDE5MDJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"82 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-843f838145cfd4750fb73ebdfb57e40c_720w.gif"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1637377718.4770844","card_id":"Q_500144856","target":{"id":500144856,"title":"如何评价《一年一度喜剧大赛》喜剧作品《父亲的葬礼》？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/500144856","type":"question","created":1637324065,"answer_count":39,"follower_count":47,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3931,22839,88372,727000,775939],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4Ihq3XweqzptcqEAMaCDczNDI0NjU4IKGq3owGMAA4L0AMcgk1MDAxNDQ4NTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"82 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":